content:
Search All Text Fields in Macros

Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions (Salesforce Classic)
Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions (Lightning Experience)

User Permissions Needed: Customize Application

To let agents search all text fields:

From Setup, enter Macros in the Quick Find box.
Select Macro Settings.
Click Edit.
Select Search all macro text fields.
Click Save.

This setting enables agents to quickly find macros by searching for keywords contained in a macroâ€™s text fields.
